{"tid":1285421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我慶幸我係香港人，你呢？","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:41:28.000Z","uid":269973,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5324a32d27a1ae8ba7e3bc92b8d4a9dc7b259e","tid":1285421,"uid":269973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"每個人，都有自己的位置<br />\n互相合作又保持獨立<br />\n為了同一個目標，香港人的未來<br />\n試問世界上係邊度可以揾到第二個咁樣嘅民族？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvKHow6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvKHow6.png&h=860882f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感謝每一位在抗爭中仍然保持專業，發表客觀報導嘅記者，你地嘅每一支筆，每一張相，都係記錄緊香港人嘅歷史，並告知全世界，香港嘅真相，多謝你地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDGyvbC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDGyvbC.png&h=9d58279c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主黨胡志偉，一向被視為中立溫和，都走上前線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRrZqLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRrZqLc.png&h=0210c0f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一分錢都冇收，只有一顆救人嘅仁心就撲出黎做義工，為前線提供最重要嘅援助，連政治立場對立嘅香港人，警察受傷一樣救，無私之心值得尊敬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYVrQcg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYVrQcg.png&h=ac2cfaaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角畫家，可能佢身體有病，但心絕對冇!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHJQxqL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHJQxqL.png&h=e8e50ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教育體系染紅，政府更想用普通話取代我地嘅母語，但香港打不死，教自己的仔女分辨善惡，辯明正反。將良知一代傳一代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tanaxqT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtanaxqT.png&h=8b969a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位香港母親，在前線希望同警察講和感動數万人。有人話佢係工黨成員，又話佢係演員。你地抹黑佢係咩身份都冇用，就算佢係吸毒嘅罪犯乞衣，佢講嘅果啲說話難道不是肺腑之言嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Li2RgSC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLi2RgSC.png&h=cd3f6166&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1PwgS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1PwgS2.png&h=ada3d442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感謝每一個曾經站在前線的弟兄，簡陋的裝備，最大的風險，你們是整個運動中最辛苦，壓力最大，付出最多的一群。感謝你們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DhNzEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DhNzEr.png&h=aa774464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感謝香港嘅法律界仍然能夠保有良知。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YARuNZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYARuNZP.png&h=ac79f52a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這一位香港人因為搬一箱水路過，被警察暴力壓制，畫面暴戾，讓全世界人見到香港警察如何醜惡。希望你早日康復。也告訴那些造謠的人，我們用的物資就是這些人自掏腰包搬過來的，絕不是什麼外國勢力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPoSrF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPoSrF.png&h=dffb02ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n癌症伯伯中槍倒地，後來仍然接受採訪希望人們繼續加油抗爭。伯伯你都加油，唔好輸俾癌症，你打緊嘅仗仲辛苦過我地，一個也不能少，加油!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjTMQdw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjTMQdw.png&h=135486f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這次運動之後，身邊很多朋友發誓再也不侮辱基督徒，天主教徒。沒有他們通宵高唱的聖歌保護，那一夜可能我們早已頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHQWs0q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHQWs0q.png&h=3129a1c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你呢？700萬人，總有你嘅位置，你為香港企左係邊呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNOti7v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNOti7v.png&h=a8bc3dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後一張，不作描述。<br />\n佢地為香港，勇往直前。"},{"pid":"e7eef923877dc4c5c46f2bcf7700ea53a2375cc5","tid":1285421,"uid":87739,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"點解？香港人無自由無民主㗎喎"},{"pid":"c660452b5a14a4ef472c3dfb8111fbbd6802bf3c","tid":1285421,"uid":269973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:37:44.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打！你整得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[文宣圖 想攞自便] 佢為香港 我為香港 幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4c8450bfa0beaaa731fbd0e388fd08e5b86b6fd","tid":1285421,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1da6a3150594436649712db6b663ac7385bc3458","tid":1285421,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7eef923877dc4c5c46f2bcf7700ea53a2375cc5","tid":1285421,"uid":87739,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"點解？香港人無自由無民主㗎喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"$0.3"},{"pid":"450b78af5e414c060ab1e18835b9564398d70d46","tid":1285421,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VecJSu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVecJSu1.jpg&h=53f04a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FZPNW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FZPNW0.png&h=462f3b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDsYGg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDsYGg0.jpg&h=7ae1e84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vM0jqJ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvM0jqJ6.jpg&h=0a757883&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a57355cd531a11398b887e8462fe69d5f715ddcf","tid":1285421,"uid":162272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"改題 -&gt; 我慶幸我唔係班港豬，你呢？"},{"pid":"274726d7fbd48ec062e0413416f503859ccb57bd","tid":1285421,"uid":36730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00322e5ed4fd4f2f00945e8cc8797ac6c77d6de","tid":1285421,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"954e8b2ebcf77cb6dd2640728d57a70eea880ff5","tid":1285421,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6160cbd3c52c54174813ca505706453644cda3","tid":1285421,"uid":261773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"我無野講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}